Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救下ZERO的Knightmare呢？
