Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才提過的中華聯邦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那我也找他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 那機師是巴別塔的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為卜部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姓名等要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你們可以視他為我們的支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他使用了Geass嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了C.C. 關於皇帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那機師的事對我也要保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係吧 有些事我也想保密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是以ZERO的身份 還是以魯路修的身份？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與你的關係同樣沒有公之於眾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 別用這種奇怪的說法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在組織內只有我們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:00:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和以前一樣繼續當ZERO親衛隊隊長行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass的事稍後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 現在應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好懷念的團員服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然準備這麼周全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紅月隊長和卜部先生讓準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 卜部光榮戰死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去告白不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告 告什麼白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO ZERO？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若不是你背叛 我們也不會被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是該解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是為了戰勝布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒別的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辯解啊謝罪什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你是為了勝利才這麼做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是以結果為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時作戰策略內容必須保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們需要他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他的才能為我平生僅見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 相信ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 ZERO視你為棋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了他誰能做到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和布里塔尼亞打仗 連中華聯邦都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EU不也在修奈澤爾皇子面前節節敗退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是所有殖民區的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了獲得獨立戰爭的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的領袖非ZERO莫屬
