Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木朱雀 就是那個抓住ZERO的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色死神還上學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是第七騎士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜是11區人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂啦 皇帝陛下直屬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木卿借配屬11區的機會 同時復學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時先坐在魯路修旁邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 你曾是我的第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 戰爭拆散了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次太平洋戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞對日本展開鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰敗國日本淪為布里塔尼亞的殖民區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被故國捨棄的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被迫捨棄故國的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重逢之時 已互為敵我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身為日本人 卻加入了布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我是ZERO 彼此隱瞞真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兵戎相向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}然而 這只是真實的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}皇帝陛下所替換的記憶有三件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}娜娜莉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於ZERO的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我曾是布里塔尼亞皇子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 現在的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真懷念啊 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀君 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你陞官了啊 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說朱雀君回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 現在還在上課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,1200)}就會在這種時候裝正經
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)}失算了吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只聽到魯路修這名字就徑直走到我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即是說 你的行動暴露了你認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來只要羅洛不輕舉妄動…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 除了我們大家都回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連老師都是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回布里塔尼亞本土？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以這裡認識朱雀的只有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 難怪都是沒見過的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你見過ZERO的臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說是克洛維斯殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪國的王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微透露點也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是軍事…嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帶來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是喜歡貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接觸下來有何疑點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 可以判斷對象的記憶仍未恢復…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有必要再調查一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不相信我們的監視？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有C.C.的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就和以前一樣繼續演弟弟的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會似乎要舉辦樞木卿歡迎會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會上再度確認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以相信魯路修嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:08:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 可以無視關於我和羅洛的一切不正常因素嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個 不要老在外面晃悠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的成員就只有維蕾塔老師了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但還有樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要殺掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別做那種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口氣別這麼彆扭好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是兄弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 為了你我也會加緊計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成功的 日本獨立這種小事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕從這學校都能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巖手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和歌山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山口也發來了報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO剛出現就這副慘狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德卿不在可能也有影響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去還會影響櫻石（Sakuradite）的供給…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}MRF: Mufti-Role Fighter 多用途戰鬥機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未確認MRF出現在內部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 這裡可是管轄11區的政廳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是鬆懈到無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11區的防線 就這程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這判斷還算馬馬虎虎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖不知何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那武裝是優先保護建築的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 這架機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可變KMF Tristan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第三騎士 齊諾·溫伯格卿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 來測試你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 阻止我試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我們也不甘就此受辱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 認真點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止 勝負已決
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是身為第七騎士的判斷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齊諾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來不是拜託你幫我送Lancelot來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 下周和羅伊德伯爵一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你怎麼穿這身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回學校了嘛 這是校服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齊諾 再怎麼名門貴族也得表現得正常點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 好重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mordred
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連阿尼婭都來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不玩啦 朱雀不讓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 戰鬥力已是綽綽有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修 三天後的歡迎會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓一切真相大白吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始第七騎士歡迎會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主賓致詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…非說不可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 這是會長命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧 在學校她就是校規
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經想開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22\fad(500,0)}（阿修弗德學園週年祭）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎馬體驗區這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我覺得這好像偏離主旨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米蕾會長就這樣 喜歡搞活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也算是去年的復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 還是把哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 那樣很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喏 要這樣 這麼拿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 我的Geass有弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尼婭 你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就參觀一下庶民學校怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 現在在校舍下的倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,備用能量填充裝置放哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}大鬍子\N這是我的\N不准碰不准打開\N敢拿走我就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尼娜的？這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過九州的基層組織F
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和迪哈爾特取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 讓拉克夏塔來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要做世界第一的批薩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我詳情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一的批薩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼這樣 來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須回收那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要執著於那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真強硬啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白自己的立場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝想抓我 以你為誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 朱雀也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個Geass無效的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到成熟御姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豐儉由人的游泳部咖啡店 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請老師來參加真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莉 待會兒要把你千刀萬剮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是任務誰當什麼老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前當過學校老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認了紅蓮二式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮在總領事館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 真難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說那邊是抵抗組織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼娜很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也在學會發表了論文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算完成Ganymede嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道？尼娜的專攻和羅伊德先生不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊德伯爵說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了推遲婚期竟不惜留級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為一個人而言本身就有很多問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞瑟 那是尤菲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀君 主角要在這裡待機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用Knightmare…做巨大批薩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給予皇帝Geass的和告訴朱雀真相的是同一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 但知道更多的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經捲進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V.V.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V.V.？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀也有Geass了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那應該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 維蕾塔老師好像在躲我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想讓魯魯幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才不是在和誰說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 這裡只有我們兩個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 感覺是個機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 魯魯 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我聽不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想幹什麼 你也不能被人看見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來帶那批薩女回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的話 在番茄堆裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連整個集裝箱一起搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽籐堂或者扇的指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰啊 太無禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等失態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別裝啞 說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話我不就暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莉 那個生物是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見亞瑟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把我寶貴的羽毛筆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 貓跟番茄搭不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起點是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…齊諾？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 庶民學校真好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是 亞瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 要改變計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 似乎已經走上遊行路線了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會在環繞校舍一周後來這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是舊式Knight 狀態還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 路線確認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shake Time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太失態了 批薩女會被帶上舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少露個臉來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我的專長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七騎士 樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴著安第斯產的特級番茄閃亮登場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正等著…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面換人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全局指揮小組
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看屋頂花園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系統模式 紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系統模式 紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始噴出滅火用瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 原來是為了玩這種驚喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記錄 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這種中斷方式也挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 見到卡蓮的是游泳部的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維蕾塔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過挺奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像是上次文化祭跟扇先生在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維蕾塔和扇？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是南先生說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直屬扇先生的地下協助人員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇？對我保密…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對這種事真是遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 倒戈了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維蕾塔·紐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以揭發ZERO真面目的功績獲得男爵之位的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是背後卻與黑色騎士團串通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種背叛行為我不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他的關係被揭穿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會失去來之不易的爵位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要重生為新的自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是夏莉讓我保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是送你的好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維蕾塔老師 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來又欠了你一次人情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是使用了外交特權而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也想盡快還你的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 再拜託你一件事行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和你共謀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和大宦官取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下攻略朱雀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主角要待在主舞台上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大家玩得挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我有話想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為第一騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 那可是帝國最高騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一騎士有特權獲得一個喜歡的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算選擇日本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了最重要的朋友和無可替代的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再失去任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要獲得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 日本人已經不需要ZERO了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間接統治嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目標是保護國？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案你問這個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周赴任的11區新總督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區一個學生向總督問話？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是樞木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 現在就在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷腦筋啊 跟那種大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上要去那邊當總督了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是娜娜莉
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻娜娜莉就在電話另一端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉知道我就是ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以朱雀才會對我用這一招
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我和娜娜莉說話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就知道我恢復記憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟以娜娜莉為圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以娜娜莉…朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼裝出一副朋友的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的本性都是將我賣給皇帝的畜牲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不配待在娜娜莉的身邊
